I think it would be cool if we ended up in G1. but hey, how about this( if 
it's sucks, so what. sue me.I think it rules.) what if all the gods, 
demigods, fates,nymphs, furies, titans, etc of antiquity were transformers. 
what if dragons that terrorized the countryside went back to their caves and 
transformed into robots. what if they were just factions protecting the seeds 
of the simple protohumans they once watched over, or using the simple minded 
hairless apes that they once thought useless. just a suggestion.

--part1_80.168c77d5.2983738f_boundary
